## DEPLOYMENT

### Cron Jobs

```cron
# Grid analysis (every 2 hours)
0 */2 * * * /path/to/scripts/run_analysis.sh

# Screener (daily at 00:00 UTC)
0 0 * * * /path/to/scripts/run_screener.sh

# Health check (every 30 seconds)
* * * * * /path/to/scripts/health_check.sh
* * * * * sleep 30; /path/to/scripts/health_check.sh

# Daily report (00:05 UTC)
5 0 * * * python -m custom_modules.telegram_bot send_daily_report
```

### Systemd Service

```ini
[Unit]
Description=Akıllı Grid Trading Bot
After=network.target

[Service]
Type=simple
User=trader
WorkingDirectory=/home/trader/trading-bot
ExecStart=/usr/bin/python3 main.py
Restart=always
RestartSec=10

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```

